revision.text: hyper graeco latin square design Le plan carré hyper gréco-latinest une plan en blocs qui déclare 4 variables de parasite ( variables nuisibles) en plus de la variable de traitement. hyper graeco-latin square design is ablock design which declares 4 blocking variables (aka nuisance variables) in addition to the treatment variable Jean-Marc Meunier Philippe Rocca-Serra Adapted from: http://www.itl.nist.gov/div898/handbook/pri/section3/pri3321.htm and no example found in pubmed->not in use in the community is a subclass from http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0500000 is a subclass from http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/OBI_0500007
